{"tid":1808634,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"理大入口設入閘機　學生教職員拍卡才可進入　學生校董李傲然斥如監控學生","createTime":"2020-01-02T13:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T05:43:40.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a57653dce4415366f2f972b5a7d3954103da7a6c","tid":1808634,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T13:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/poly-29_VgySe_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpoly-29_VgySe_1200x0.png&h=17536d4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n理工大學去年11月爆發激烈警民衝突，事件中校園大量設置被破壞，復修需時。理大預料本月13日展開第二學期，校方最近重新開放校園部份範圍，其中A座附近的入口增設了入閘機，要求出入的學生和教職員拍卡方能進入。從相片所見，A座附近的入口約有9部入閘機，暫時用黃色的膠板圍封，有人員安裝及測試入閘機。理大學生校董李傲然對校方做法表示非常不滿，形容此舉是限制學生出入、監控學生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/WhatsApp20Image202020-01-0220at208.43.2220PM_K8HZW_1200x0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FWhatsApp20Image202020-01-0220at208.43.2220PM_K8HZW_1200x0.jpeg&h=1a998720&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有教職員透露，Y座位置亦設有入閘機，估計入閘機將會在理工大學各個出入口裝設，估計待1月13日學生回校考試前投入服務。另外，有相片亦顯示連接紅墈站的天橋入口兩旁鋪設鐵絲網，入口位置設有尖刺的大閘。<br />\n<br />\n理大學生校董李傲然對校方做法表示非常不滿，形容此舉是限制學生出入，禁控學生出入時間。他認為，大學是自由開放的地方，不認同任何方式阻礙門口，又指紅墈站連接大學校園的天橋裝了鐵閘，是將大學重重圍困的表現，長遠影響理工大學在國際間的形象。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，校方在此事上從來沒有諮詢學生意見，「完全是自把自為，影響校方及學生關係，本身關係其實已經好差，現時係將矛盾激化，極不可取。」他指，現階段未有下一步行動，需與學生商討後再作決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/理大入口設入閘機-學生教職員拍卡才可進入-學生校董李傲然斥如監控學生/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%A3%E8%A8%AD%E5%85%A5%E9%96%98%E6%A9%9F-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%95%99%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E6%8B%8D%E5%8D%A1%E6%89%8D%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%A0%A1%E8%91%A3%E6%9D%8E%E5%82%B2%E7%84%B6%E6%96%A5%E5%A6%82%E7%9B%A3%E6%8E%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%2F&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPoCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=d7e15657\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%A3%E8%A8%AD%E5%85%A5%E9%96%98%E6%A9%9F-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%95%99%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E6%8B%8D%E5%8D%A1%E6%89%8D%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%A0%A1%E8%91%A3%E6%9D%8E%E5%82%B2%E7%84%B6%E6%96%A5%E5%A6%82%E7%9B%A3%E6%8E%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%2F&h=74b7a57b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/理大入口設入閘機-學生教職員拍卡才可進入-學生校董李傲然斥如監控學生/</a>"},{"pid":"185b2772dadfc0ca0319ade47f47acaf7899dfa2","tid":1808634,"uid":33749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T13:24:36.000Z","msg":"poly地下嗰層好似係公共空間嚟嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c9dbb02db9df38e8288242a3e991d352ccf371","tid":1808634,"uid":33984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T13:29:07.000Z","msg":"BU 都係"},{"pid":"9a7bfec3cf0a1f988e1bc8ab3a12c0caf81dc997","tid":1808634,"uid":67816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T13:33:08.000Z","msg":"學埋中國d大學hall唔准鎖門要隨時比人入去檢查啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95432b6f308e7b56ab6fcd2d23f8fabc58a43179","tid":1808634,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:40:20.000Z","msg":"其實入閘機單嘢<br />\n要廣傳外國㗎<br />\n<br />\n因為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大學一向就係自由嘅象徵</span></span><br />\n文明國家好重視<br />\n搞大學好多都好難接受<br />\n當日中大 理大就係咁<br />\n<br />\n英文tweet<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LrMdpAE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLrMdpAE.jpg&h=f446163a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/39zHxDv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F39zHxDv&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPoCLuB